792
00:55:25,970 --> 00:55:28,060
Prosím vás o túto láskavosť, doktor Jin.

793
00:55:28,970 --> 00:55:30,630
Slečna...

794
00:55:39,520 --> 00:55:41,380
Ako to dopadlo?

795
00:55:44,200 --> 00:55:45,470
Odpovedzte mi!

796
00:55:45,480 --> 00:55:47,850
