799
00:56:00,210 --> 00:56:02,620
Je to pravda?

800
00:56:02,620 --> 00:56:04,170
Áno.

801
00:56:04,170 --> 00:56:06,840
Nie je to rakovina prsníka.

802
00:56:08,860 --> 00:56:11,910
Moja pani, čo som vám hovoril ...

803
